The paper deals with downlink pilot assignment in cell-free massive MIMO systems, which involves the use of information theory, networking, and signal processing concepts. Therefore, cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), and cs.SY (Systems and Control) are likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper focuses on massive MIMO, which is a subfield of wireless communication and falls under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.COM (Computer Communications and Networks).
